      "span_text": "For drug efficacy studies using a GEMM of lung cancer, Kras LSL-G12D/+ and Trp53 fl/fl mice (8-12 weeks old) were anaesthetized by intraperitoneal injection of ketamine (80 mg per kg body weight) and xylazine (10 mg per kg body weight) and infected intratracheally with 2.5 × 10 5 infectious particles of Lenti-Cre per mouse, as previously described"
